  "id": "api/common/formatDate",
  "title": "formatDate",
  "contents": "<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/common/formatDate\", \"name\": \"formatDate\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/common/src/i18n/format_date.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L42-L115\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/15.0.1/packages/common/src/i18n/format_date.ts#L42-L115\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"formatdate\">formatDate<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/formatDate#formatdate\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p>Formats a date according to locale rules.</p>\n<p>基于区域规则格式化日期。</p>\n\n  </section>\n\n  <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/common/formatDate\" class=\"code-anchor\">formatDate</a></span>(value: string | number | Date, format: string, locale: string, timezone?: string): string</code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"参数\">参数</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>value</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string | number | Date</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p>The date to format, as a Date, or a number (milliseconds since UTC epoch)\nor an <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/NOTE-datetime\">ISO date-time string</a>.</p>\n<p>要格式化的日期，是一个日期、数字（从 UTC 时代以来的毫秒数）或 ISO 字符串\n(<a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/NOTE-datetime\">https://www.w3.org/TR/NOTE-datetime</a>)。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>format</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p>The date-time components to include. See <code><a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">DatePipe</a></code> for details.</p>\n<p>表示要包含的日期/时间部件。欲知详情，参见 <code><a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">DatePipe</a></code>。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>locale</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p>A locale code for the locale format rules to use.</p>\n<p>一个区域代码，用来表示要使用的区域格式规则。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>timezone</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p>The time zone. A time zone offset from GMT (such as <code>'+0430'</code>),\nor a standard UTC/GMT or continental US time zone abbreviation.\nIf not specified, uses host system settings.</p>\n<p>时区。可以是 GMT 中的时区偏移（如 <code>'+0430'</code>），或一个标准的 UTC/GMT 或美国大陆时区的缩写。\n如果没有指定，就会使用宿主系统中的设定。</p>\n\n        <p>可选值。默认值为 <code>undefined</code>。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"返回值\">返回值</h6>\n  <p><code>string</code>: The formatted date string.</p>\n<p>格式化之后的日期字符串。</p>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">参见<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/formatDate#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><p><code><a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">DatePipe</a></code></p></li>\n    <li><p><a href=\"https://angular.io/guide/i18n-overview\">Internationalization (i18n) Guide</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"guide/i18n-overview\">国际化 (i18n) 指南</a></p></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/DatePipe\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common\n - api/common/DatePipe\n - api/common/formatDate#formatdate\n - api/common/formatDate#see-also\n - guide/i18n-overview\n - https://angular.io/guide/i18n-overview\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/common/src/i18n/format_date.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L42-L115\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/15.0.1/packages/common/src/i18n/format_date.ts#L42-L115\n - https://www.w3.org/TR/NOTE-datetime\n-->"
